race.comment: TURN UP THE MUSIC (4) improved last time out to score by 1.1L here this trip and will hit this at peak for the sharp Currie barn. Has a handy 2kg claim today and will use the inside gate. Nicely placed to keep the ball rolling. COMMAND APPROVED (2) showed good early speed before fading beaten 3.5 lengths over 1200m on the Gold Coast Poly. Won there prior and the claimer will position him forward from a soft barrier. He has won here and is in the mix. KWAMI (3) is on a quick return and is proven third-up. Is back in grade with a 2kg claim and deserves consideration. SAGA'S GIRL (12) was an easy maiden winner fresh and solid here last time. Can feature.
